	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/03/31/morning-agenda-the-dewey-seven-pleas-unsealed/" data-title="The &#8216;Dewey Seven&#8217; Pleas, Unsealed" data-description="The pleas of seven former employees of Dewey &amp; LeBoeuf have been unsealed. | Comcast&#039;s chief executive is looking beyond cable. | Is Facebook too big to care? | A lawyer takes on fiduciary failures. | The author Michael Lewis is taking aim at high-speed traders.">
